cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM 

The paper deals with semantic segmentation, which is a computer vision task, hence cs.CV is the most likely category. The paper also proposes an end-to-end deep learning approach, which involves metric learning, making cs.LG and cs.AI likely categories as well. The paper also discusses the interpretability of the results, which is a topic of interest in natural language processing (NLP) and computer vision (CV), making cs.CL a possible category. Finally, the paper discusses the precision of the boundaries and consistency of region predictions, which are topics of interest in multimedia (MM), making it a possible category as well.
